-- pd.package: Roboto - fpm font
name: fifthtry.github.io/Roboto

This component consist of Google Roboto font with all it's styles from Thin-100 to Black-900 Italic.


-- pd.component: Roboto - fpm font
name: https://github.com/FifthTry/roboto

This component consist of Google Roboto font with all it's styles from Thin-100 to Black-900 Italic.



-- tf.h3: How to use

include fifthtry.github.io/roboto package into FPM.ftd file

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/roboto as roboto

\-- fpm.auto-import: roboto


-- tf.markdown:

Inside your .ftd file to change for any specific token use:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- import: fifthtry.github.io/roboto/assets as roboto-assets
\-- import: fpm

\-- How to: define a custom font:-

\-- ftd.type roboto-font-desktop:
size.px: 40
weight: 900
font-family: $roboto-assets.fonts.Roboto


\-- ftd.type roboto-font-mobile:
size.px: 40
weight: 900
font-family: $roboto-assets.fonts.Roboto


\-- ftd.responsive-type roboto-font:
desktop: $roboto-font-desktop
mobile: $roboto-font-mobile


\-- How to: invoke a custom font:-

\-- ftd.text: Todos os seres humanos nascem livres e iguais em dignidade.  
